Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to start our field trip here,\Nin the world famous Canterlot Sculpture Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That one over there\Nrepresents friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, my little ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This one represents victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool would it be to have\N*that* for a cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were actually\Nvictoryful at somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you? A dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is a really interesting statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you notice about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got an eagle claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-And a lion paw!\N-And a snake tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This creature is called a draconequus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the head of a pony and a body\Nmade up of all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose that represents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Confusion!\N-Evil!\N-Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not chaos, you dodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me things\NI don't know the meaning of!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is too chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:00:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, in a way you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This statue represents discord...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...which means a lack of\Nharmony between ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you three have\Ndemonstrated discord so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you're each going to\Nwrite me an essay explaining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go. And I don't\Nwant any more fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's confusion!\N-Evil!\N-Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeew! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! It's not supposed\Nto rain until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I didn't tell you to go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! What's\Ngoing on with that rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... chocolate milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... chocolate milk rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's crazy weather\Nall over Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale's getting soaked\Nby a major cola storm right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. I'm not leaving you,\Ntill I get control of Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you wanna stop *this*?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about your troubles, Applejack,\Nand I came to see if there's anything I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Without getting wet. Or dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or out from under my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Do somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Angel, you really shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be seeing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, everyone! I've learned\Na new spell that'll fix everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My fail-safe spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...failed! What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike. Twilight will come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow! Can you corral all those\Nclouds in one corner of the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! I need you to bring those\Nhigh strong storm clouds down to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear! I hope that none\Nof the animals see these...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...delicious chocolate-filled\Ncotton candy clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to have to share them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me both, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when y'all are done that, feel free\Nto have some popcorn for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Spike? You\Nshould never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can't\Novercome if we all work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls! Princess Celestia wants\Nto see us all in Canterlot immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia! We came\Nas fast as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight. Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this about the weather?\NAnd the animals' weird behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening out there? Why\Nisn't my magic working? Is there...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've called you here\Nfor a matter of great importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems an old foe of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...someone I thought I had\Ndefeated long ago, has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord is the mischievous\Nspirit of disharmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my sister and I\Nstood up to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...he ruled Equestria in an eternal state\Nof unrest and unhappiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna and I saw how miserable\Nlife was for earth ponies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...pegasi and unicorns alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So after discovering\Nthe Elements of Harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...we combined our powers\Nand rose up against him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...turning him to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the spell we cast would\Nkeep him contained forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...but since Luna and I are\Nno longer connected to the Elements...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...the spell has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No longer connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Canterlot tower, where\Nthe Elements are kept inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...since all of you recovered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to wield the Elements of Harmony\Nonce again and stop Discord...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...before he thrusts\Nall of Equestria into eternal chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But why us? Why don't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! We're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You six showed the full\Npotential of the Elements...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...by harnessing the magic of your\Nfriendship to beat a mighty foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Luna and I\Nonce wielded the Elements...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...it is you, who now control their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is you, who must defeat Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia, you can count on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal chaos comes with\Nchocolate rain, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,CHOCOLATE RAIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to her, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be honored to use\Nthe Elements of Harmony again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can keep the Elements.\NI'll take that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no fear, ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have total confidence that you\Nwill be able to defeat Discord...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. If anyone needs me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll be outside in the chocolate\Npuddles with a giant swizzle straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements! They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That chamber is protected by\Na powerful spell that only I can break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Make sense"? Oh, what fun\Nis there in making sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you miss me, Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite lonely being encased in stone.\NBut you wouldn't know that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't turn ponies into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! What have you done\Nwith the Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just borrowed them\Nfor a teensy little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get away\Nwith this, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd forgotten how grim\Nyou can be, Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really quite boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nopony insults the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You must be Rainbow Dash...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...famed for her loyalty ‒ the Element\Nof Harmony you represent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'll always\Nbe loyal to the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're wasting our time\Ntalking to a tacky window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The beautiful Rarity, representing\Nthe Element of Generosity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I'm not mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know who we are. Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know much more than\Nthat, honest Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to know our strengths too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And yours is the most powerful\Nand elusive element ‒ magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's is kindness and Pinkie Pie's\Nis the personal favorite of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's standing on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop stalling, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done with\Nthe Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So boring, Celestia. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll tell you, but\NI'll only tell you my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To retrieve your missing elements,\Njust make sense of this change of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns are my master plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...then find the Elements\Nback where you began.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you reckon he meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Twists and turns" and then\Nthe "back where we started".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Discord hid the Elements\Nin the palace labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, my little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of Equestria is in your hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Princess. We won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We... We have to go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Dopey Discord\Nforgot about these babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just do a quick flyover and\Nwe'll have the Elements in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You should see the looks\Non your faces. Priceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us our wings and horns back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get them back in good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply took them to ensure\Nthere's no cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this is the first\Nrule of our game:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No flying and no magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The first rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The second rule is: everypony has to play\Nor the game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Never fear, girls. We have each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Like Twilight said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can't overcome\Nif we all stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, girls! Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony head to the middle as fast as\Nyou can and we'll regroup there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Moving out!\N-See you in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeehaw!\N-See you guys there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! Who's there?! GIIIRLS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are y'all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The keepers of the grove of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You may ask us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...a one question:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Past, future or present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But be warned...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...that the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...may not always be pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then. I don't trust\Nthis place for the hill a' beans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I got a real bad feelin'\Nabout this feller Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna come of this\Nhere mission we're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For the answer you seek...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...go ahead! Take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I'll never see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Fine!\N-Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's settled then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friendship... over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true. It just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That just can't be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When all the truth does...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...is make your heart ache...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...sometimes a lie is easier to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! Thank goodness.\NI thought I heard voices over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talkin' to, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony! Nopony whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Uh, we best be goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Applejack just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight.\NApplejack wouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest\Nballoon garden I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first balloon garden\NI've ever seen, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Pinkie Pie?\NI thought you appreciated a good laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different. They're\Nlaughing *at* me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends laugh at you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends laugh *with* me, not at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought\Nlaughter made you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Are we glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, huh? WHY? Need a good laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose has her\Nso upset? It's not like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice anythin'\Nstrange about Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird. Better pick up the pace before\Nthe stress of this gets the better of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting an audience with\Nthe Princess, not outdoor sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to your lucky day, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found the one thing in Equestria\Nthat could rival my face for sheer beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I like very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,NO! No. I shan't succumb\Nto such fabulousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Must... get to the center...\Nto meet... the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,MINE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Rarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It took forever, but it was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew three little gemstones would turn out\Nto be this handsome HUNK of a diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Are we glad to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you carrying\Na humongous boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "boulder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This big, beautiful, bedazzling\Nrock is a DIAMOND!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your envious little eyes off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it and it's mine,\Nfair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I can do this. I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Butterflies? Wait! Don't leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've been left behind\Nby your so-called friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm certain they're\Ndoing their best to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it must be so upsetting to know how\Nweak and helpless they think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I *am* weak and helpless and\NI appreciate their understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well... surely it burns you up, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...that they're always\Npointing out your flaws, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm awfully lucky to have friends\Nwho want me to be the best I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been kind for\Nfar too long, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to be cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrivederci!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! I'm so glad\Nto see your friendly face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This awful labyrinth is\Ngetting to everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boo hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wave your magic little horn\Nand make everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. You can't.\NYou don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening to my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are YOU laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Little help here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're welcome...\N-But don't get any ideas about my gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you now, Element.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why you like these\Nclouds so much. Very plush.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off there and put 'em up!\NC'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm here to deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a message for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely. This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:20:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A weighty choice is yours to make ‒\NThe right selection or a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If the wrong choice you choose to pursue,\NThe foundations of home will crumble without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale? Crumble... without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That box contains your wings.\NYou can take them and leave the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...or you can carry on aimlessly\Nwandering this maze. Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Must... find... Rainbow Dash...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As a team... we're unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash won't let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, lookie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash is flyin' away.\NShe's abandonin' us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well. Somepony broke\Nthe "no wings, no magic" rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Game's over, my little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't find your precious elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we might be due\Nfor a big old storm of chaos.
